Package: rmoriebricklayer
Title: Reproducible Data Bundles with Provenance and Fallback
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Vansh Singh", "Ruhela", email = "vsruhela@proton.me",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-1750-3592"))
Description: Tools for building brick-proof, reproducible data bundles.
    Resolves open-data sources through CKAN package_show and
    package_search endpoints, records and verifies provenance with SHA256
    digests and Wayback Machine snapshots, validates downloaded data
    against a pinned schema, and falls back to schema-driven synthetic
    data when the real source is unreachable. Run records are captured in
    a manifest plus a plain-language summary so any result can be traced
    back to its inputs.
